He picks up his razor again, examining the edge.

"Seven years she lay quiet in the crypt below the palace. Then she woke. Wrong. Not herself. Not human." He draws a finger across his throat. "They sealed the palace after that. But she gets out sometimes. Into the district. People die."

&gt;</result>
