    <item nodeId="node-1937">
        <command xml:space="preserve">move</command>
        <result xml:space="preserve">Before you can settle in, two large men grab you by the arms and haul you toward the door. "Get out, freak," one of them growls. You do not resist. There is nothing here worth a fight.

You are back on the street.

